attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: Introducing a developer’s dream in South Boston’s coveted East Side. 607 East 7th Street, a 3-family, and neighboring 611 (MLS#), a 2-family, offer over 7,000 sq. ft. of combined prime land with off-street parking and 4 deeded parking spaces in one of the city’s hottest markets. Ideal for a luxury condo conversion, upscale rentals, or a signature single-family estate, this package delivers the size, location, and demand every developer seeks. Steps to the beach, the newly renovated Curley Community Center (free for residents), award-winning dining, and vibrant nightlife. Enjoy quick access to Route 90, I-93, and Downtown Boston, with Logan Airport and the Seaport only 15 minutes away. With South Boston’s market at record highs, this is a rare chance to build in a high-demand district. Seller prefers to convey both properties together. Buyers to perform all due diligence.
